data.description: Look no further! Are you ready to leave the city and enjoy the serenity of the country. This pristine 4/2 home situated on 8.44 acres offers just that! Enjoy the large 1/2 acre pond . This home offers a large deck on the front and back of the home for all your entertaining needs. Just over 2,300 sq ft this country home has plenty of space for you and your family! Offering (2) living rooms, an open concept kitchen and 4 bedrooms, this home has everything you could need/want. Brand new HVAC unit installed in 2021 and a  new metal roof installed in 2017. You will notice a 30x20 barn that was started but not yet completed. The sellers will be leaving all building materials for completion with the sell!  This home will not last long!
